都叫唔好提港獨，你地唱反調唔合作人地點幫？同外國互相合作先可以達到目標，但一但比中共切斷晒外國幫助，就會撤底輸。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:48:28.000Z","msg":"其實係咁叫光復香港個班人根本想帶風向搞死個運動。<br />\n<br />\n中共一直就係想扣香港人暴徒帽子，從而阻止晒外國干涉大條道理鎮壓你地，所以你地做乜都話你暴徒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實係咁叫________個班人根本想帶風向搞死個運動。<br />\n<br />\n中共一直就係想扣香港人____帽子，從而阻止晒外國干涉大條道理鎮壓你地，所以你地做乜都話你____。<br />\n<br />\n泛民打手收皮啦，想帶風向？"},{"pid":"d0a894be206faea563da0f72d4514fd2f25f5624","tid":1810672,"uid":160964,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:48:44.000Z","msg":"612開始已經係搞緊港獨革命，樓主唔好咁天真<br />\n勇武派好大部分都係想港獨"},{"pid":"e79ffc6e7e731bb0cb2df62f5ec1ddad3856ceaa","tid":1810672,"uid":267823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:49:12.000Z","msg":"又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18eb8b79317cd47358f40ec28ef3bbf59107959d","tid":1810672,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a0edad43b837ee12c0325ba5c3f1d57c0cee37ea","tid":1810672,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d6cf5de03c812f53e90003f14ed7b1511e80cc6","tid":1810672,"uid":94982,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:41:45.000Z","msg":"班人一向受情感驅動，眼中只有自己想點，低估狗同中共既邪惡，以為對面好廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:44:19.000Z","msg":"恐懼係咪一種情感？<br />\n驚激嬲共產黨所以綁手綁腳個班係咪受情感驅動？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:49:25.000Z","msg":"繼續提港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未嬴中共主動惹起十幾億中國人反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對家都識統戰次要敵人打首要敵人，我地反而越多敵人越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df2bafaec2360b10c60c7d54f8fb04f069825ce5","tid":1810672,"uid":145296,"like":1,"disli