"uid":116054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:58:14.000Z","msg":"鎮壓我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一直想攬炒，中共一定唔驚香港樓市股市冧"},{"pid":"080f5479c5d872fdd56112ceef63d46baabf6090","tid":1810672,"uid":105166,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b913b175ff617d7bb8912e3ea5d1d30a0e3fc99b","tid":1810672,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"845bce81039c8875868c85e39cec3f5676b3d176","tid":1810672,"uid":59297,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:45:46.000Z","msg":"得啦，同一個論調洗唔洗係咁loop<br />\n<br />\n獨派係鬼，天琦係鬼，得未呀？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:46:42.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n不停重覆討論同一個問題係咩事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:58:26.000Z","msg":"因為泛民先係真正保皇黨，佢地要keep住個政權，先做到反對派。你另立政權，佢會冇嘢撈，or好大風險冇嘢撈，梗係怕你啦。元旦果日見到幾多公民黨工黨啲牌，全部都淨係敢印五大訴求，連光復香港都唔敢印㗎，佢地食人血饅頭㗎咋，唔好當晒佢地係咩好人"},{"pid":"2f0318b932b2d90f6289af6c5cb4a216c40efcdb","tid":1810672,"uid":23400,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ca42a6e87a750330b8de33e1ea93918c7fea640e","tid":1810672,"uid":117225,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"18eb8b79317cd47358f40ec28ef3bbf59107959d","tid":1810672,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a0edad43b837ee12c0325ba5c3f1d57c0cee37ea","tid":1810672,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:44:19.000Z","msg":"恐懼係咪一種情感？<br />\n驚激嬲共產黨所以綁手綁腳個班係咪受情感驅動？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:49:25.000Z","msg":"繼續提港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未嬴中共主動惹起十幾億中國人反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對家都識統戰次要敵人打首要敵人，我地反而越多敵人越好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T05:53:53.000Z","msg":"十幾億人理你老味咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog